Random number generation with unique values
================================================

*) User needs to generate 6 digits random values. 
*) To generate with unique values without duplicates. 


Code:
=======
VB.NET
=====
 Dim rnd As New Random()
 Dim count as integer = 400000
 Dim uniqueNumbers As List(Of Integer) = Enumerable.Range(100000, 900000) _
 .OrderBy(Function(x) rnd.Next()) _
 .Take(count) _
 .ToList()
 For i as Integer =0 to uniqueNumbers.count-1
 Console.WriteLine(uniqueNumbers(i).ToString())
 Next
